---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const title = "BestMyTest TOEFL Review 2026: The Best Value for Practice?";
const description = "Read our honest BestMyTest TOEFL review. We analyze the 2,000+ practice questions and 20 full-length tests to see if it is worth your money in 2026.";
---

<Base title={title} description={description} type="article">
  <Header />
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 text-neutral-300">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Platform Review · Updated April 2026</span>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mt-4 mb-6 leading-tight">BestMyTest TOEFL Review: The Best Value for Practice?</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">BestMyTest is an online TOEFL preparation platform that specializes in practice questions. It offers a massive library of over 2,000 practice questions and 20 full-length practice tests. The platform is designed to mimic the actual TOEFL iBT interface. This helps students feel comfortable before they sit for the real exam.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-neutral-800 border border-neutral-700 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12 shadow-xl">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between">
        <div class="mb-6 md:mb-0">
          <p class="font-bold text-lg text-white">Our Rating</p>
          <p class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-green-500">8.8/10</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-right">
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 font-bold uppercase">Best For</p>
          <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Realistic practice tests</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">What is BestMyTest?</h2>
    <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">BestMyTest is an online TOEFL preparation platform that specializes in practice questions. It offers a massive library of over 2,000 practice questions and 20 full-length practice tests. The platform is designed to mimic the actual TOEFL iBT interface. This helps students feel comfortable before they sit for the real exam. If you need a lot of practice to build your confidence, this is a strong choice.</p>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">Pricing</h2>
    <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">BestMyTest offers three main plans. The "Last Minute" plan costs $69 for one month of access. The "Premium" plan is $189 for six months. For those who need a long-term study partner, the "Custom" plan is $349 for one year. Each plan includes a score improvement guarantee. If your score does not go up, you can get your money back. This shows they are confident in their teaching method.</p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
      <div class="bg-green-900/10 border border-green-500/20 p-8 rounded-2xl">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-400 mb-4">Pros</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Over 20 full-length practice tests that look like the real exam.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Detailed feedback on your writing and speaking responses.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>A large library of lessons covering all four sections.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Score improvement guarantee for all paid plans.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-red-900/10 border border-red-500/20 p-8 rounded-2xl">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-red-400 mb-4">Cons</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-red-500 mr-2">✗</span>
            <span>The interface can feel a bit crowded with too much information.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-red-500 mr-2">✗</span>
            <span>There are no live classes: everything is self-paced.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">Verdict</h2>
    <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">BestMyTest is excellent for students who learn by doing. The number of practice tests is much higher than most competitors. However, if you want live interaction, you should look elsewhere. We recommend combining BestMyTest with a private tutor from iTalki or Preply. A tutor can help you understand the mistakes you make in the practice tests. This combination is the fastest way to reach a high score.</p>

    <div class="bg-blue-900/20 border border-blue-500/30 rounded-2xl p-8 my-12">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Start Your Preparation</h3>
      <p class="text-neutral-300">Try BestMyTest today or find a specialized TOEFL tutor on Preply to guide your study plan.</p>
    </div>
  </article>

  <script type="application/ld+json" slot="structured-data" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Review",
    "itemReviewed": {
      "@type": "SoftwareApplication",
      "name": "BestMyTest TOEFL Prep"
    },
    "reviewRating": {
      "@type": "Rating",
      "ratingValue": "8.8",
      "bestRating": "10"
    },
    "author": {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "LearnEnglish.Life"
    },
    "publisher": {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "LearnEnglish.Life"
    },
    "datePublished": "2026-04-11"
  })} />
  <Footer />
</Base>
